{"_id":"2fXfGt3S9Rzqhnkv","name":"Nightblade","type":"class","img":"modules/ffd20-content/assets/Ninja.png","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>W<em style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Candara, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.45em;\">Nightblades are fast and deadly, their blades slicing through enemies&rsquo; defenses&mdash;and throats&mdash;before they have time to react.</em></p>\n<p>The nightblade is an archetype of the ninja class.</p>\n<p>Alignment:&nbsp;Any</p>\n<p>Hit Die:&nbsp;d8</p>\n<p>Parent Classes:&nbsp;Monk and Thief.</p>\n<p>Starting Wealth:&nbsp;4d6 &times; 10 gil (average 140 gil.) In addition, each character begins play with an outfit worth 10 gil or less.</p>\n<p>Class Skills<br />The ninja&rsquo;s class skills are Acrobatics (Dex), Appraise (Int), Bluff (Cha), Climb (Str), Craft (Int), Diplomacy (Cha), Disable Device (Dex), Disguise (Cha), Escape Artist (Dex), Intimidate (Cha), Knowledge (local) (Int), Knowledge (nobility) (Int), Linguistics (Int), Perception (Wis), Perform (Cha), Profession (Wis), Sense Motive (Wis), Sleight of Hand (Dex), Stealth (Dex), Swim (Str), and Use Magic Device (Cha).</p>\n<p>Skill Points Per Level:&nbsp;8 + Int modifier</p>\n<h2>Table: Ninja</h2>\n<table id=\"tablepress-91\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"5\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Level</th>\n<th>Special</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#ac-bonus\">AC Bonus</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/archetypes/nightblade/\">Stamina Pool</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#sneak-attack\">Sneak Attack</a>&nbsp;(+1d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#limit-breaks\">Limit Breaks</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2nd</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#evasion\">Evasion,&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/archetypes/nightblade/\">Talent Trees</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#ki-pool\">Ki Pool</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#no-trace\">No Trace</a>&nbsp;+1,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#sneak-attack\">Sneak Attack</a>&nbsp;(+2d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#ninjutsu\">Ninjutsu</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/archetypes/nightblade/\">Talent Trees</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#uncanny-dodge\">Uncanny Dodge</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#sneak-attack\">Sneak Attack</a>&nbsp;(+3d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#ninjutsu\">Ninjutsu</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#light-steps\">Light Steps</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/archetypes/nightblade/\">Talent Trees</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#no-trace\">No Trace</a>&nbsp;+2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#sneak-attack\">Sneak Attack</a>&nbsp;(+4d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#ninjutsu\">Ninjutsu</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/archetypes/nightblade/\">Talent Trees</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#improved-uncanny-dodge\">Improved Uncanny Dodge</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#no-trace\">No Trace</a>&nbsp;+3,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#sneak-attack\">Sneak Attack</a>&nbsp;(+5d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#ninjutsu\">Ninjutsu</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/archetypes/nightblade/\">Talent Trees</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#cloaked-in-shadows\">Cloaked in Shadows</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#sneak-attack\">Sneak Attack</a>&nbsp;(+6d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#ninjutsu\">Ninjutsu</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>12th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/archetypes/nightblade/\">Talent Trees</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#no-trace\">No Trace</a>&nbsp;+4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#sneak-attack\">Sneak Attack</a>&nbsp;(+7d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#ninjutsu\">Ninjutsu</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>14th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/archetypes/nightblade/\">Talent Trees</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#hide-in-plain-sight\">Hide in Plain Sight</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>15th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#no-trace\">No Trace</a>&nbsp;+5,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#sneak-attack\">Sneak Attack</a>&nbsp;(+8d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#ninjutsu\">Ninjutsu</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>16th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/archetypes/nightblade/\">Talent Trees</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#sneak-attack\">Sneak Attack</a>&nbsp;(+9d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#ninjutsu\">Ninjutsu</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>18th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/archetypes/nightblade/\">Talent Trees</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#no-trace\">No Trace</a>&nbsp;+6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>19th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#shadow-step\">Shadow Step</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#sneak-attack\">Sneak Attack</a>&nbsp;(+10d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#ninjutsu\">Ninjutsu</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>20th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#hidden-master\">Hidden Master</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/archetypes/nightblade/\">Talent Trees</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>Favored Class Bonuses</h2>\n<p>Instead of receiving an additional skill rank or hit point whenever they gain a level in a favored class, some races have the option of choosing from a number of other bonuses, depending upon their favored classes. The following options are available to the listed race who have ninja as their favored class, and unless otherwise stated, the bonus applies each time you select the listed favored class reward.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/base-races/al-bhed/\">Al Bhed</a>:&nbsp;Add +1/3 on critical hit confirmation rolls made while using sneak attack (maximum bonus of +5). This bonus does not stack with Critical Focus.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/base-races/burmecian/\">Burmecian</a>:&nbsp;Add +1 to the ninja&rsquo;s base speed. In combat, this option has no effect unless the ninja has selected it five times (or another increment of five).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/dwarf/\">Dwarf</a>:&nbsp;Gain a +1/3 bonus on Knowledge (dungeoneering) checks and on Survival checks when underground. If the ninja has a +1 bonus on Knowledge (dungeoneering) checks from this ability, he is also considered trained in that skill.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/elvaan/\">Elvaan</a>:&nbsp;Gain +1/3 on all Acrobatics, Climb, and Stealth checks in forested areas.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/galka/\">Galka</a>:&nbsp;Add +1/3 on critical hit confirmation rolls made while using sneak attack (maximum bonus of +5). This bonus does not stack with Critical Focus.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/base-races/garlean/\">Garlean</a>:&nbsp;Add +1/4 point to the ninja&rsquo;s ki pool.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/half-breed/\">Half-Breed</a>:&nbsp;Add +1/4 point to the ninja&rsquo;s ki pool.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/hume/\">Hume</a>:&nbsp;Add +1/4 point to the ninja&rsquo;s ki pool.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/beastman-tribes/kojin/\">Kojin</a>:&nbsp;Add a +1/3 bonus on damage rolls to sneak attack.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/mithra/\">Mithra</a>:&nbsp;Add a +1 bonus to attack rolls when attacking on or charging from higher ground.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/moogle/\">Moogle</a>:&nbsp;Gain a +1/4 bonus to CMD against trip and on damage rolls against prone targets that add the ninja&rsquo;s Strength modifier.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/beastman-tribes/namazu/\">Namazu</a>:&nbsp;Gain +1/3 on all Acrobatics, Climb, and Stealth checks in urban areas.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/base-races/shindroid/\">Shindroid</a>:&nbsp;Add +1/4 point to the ninja&rsquo;s ki pool.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/tarutaru/\">Tarutaru</a>:&nbsp;Add +1 to the ninja&rsquo;s Acrobatics check bonus gained by spending a point from his ki pool. A ninja must be at least 5th level to select this benefit.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/base-races/viera/\">Viera</a>:&nbsp;Add +1 to the ninja&rsquo;s Acrobatics check bonus gained by spending a point from his ki pool. A ninja must be at least 5th level to select this benefit.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/beastman-tribes/yagudo/\">Yagudo</a>:&nbsp;Add a +1 bonus to attack rolls when attacking on or charging from higher ground.</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false},"links":{"children":[],"classAssociations":[{"id":"ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-ninja.5g5eBU7FrCFc3j46","dataType":"compendium","name":"Limit Break: Missile Barrage","img":"systems/ffd20/icons/FFxiv-icons/FFXIVIcons-MainCommand-(Others)/02_General/limit_break.png","level":1,"_index":0},{"id":"ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-ninja.RRALw8pq8HoRnAGj","dataType":"compendium","name":"Limit Break: Shroud in Darkness","img":"systems/ffd20/icons/FFxiv-icons/FFXIVIcons-MainCommand-(Others)/02_General/limit_break.png","level":1,"_index":1},{"id":"ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-ninja.ZHVr8GRwz17suWNV","dataType":"compendium","name":"Sneak Attack","img":"systems/ffd20/icons/FFxiv-icons/FFXIVIcon