{"_id":"4Z1T9uYvSaGqxqF2","name":"Ki Power: Ki Blade","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A ninja can expend 1 ki point as a swift action to grant any weapon she is holding a +1 enhancement bonus for 1 minute. For every four levels beyond 3rd, the weapon gains another +1 enhancement bonus, to a maximum of +5 at 19th level. These bonuses can be added to the weapon, stacking with existing weapon enhancements to a maximum of +5. Multiple uses of this ability do not stack with themselves. These bonuses do not function if the weapon is wielded by anyone other than the ninja. A ninja can only enhance one weapon in this way at one time. If she uses this ability again, the first use immediately ends.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Ki Power"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"swift"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":"1","units":"minute"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"tag":"ninjutsuKiBlade","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"abilityType":"su","attack":{},"identifiedName":"Ki Power: Ki Blade"},"flags":{"importid":"6rD4iX2VjYeu0qPg"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"55V9pftoLB6bzHms","name":"Ki Power: Replacement","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Once per day when a successful attack is made against a ninja with this ability, as an immediate action she can spend 1 ki point to attempt a Stealth check opposed by the attacker&rsquo;s Perception check. The ninja can attempt this check while being observed as long as she has cover or concealment (or an ability that allows her to attempt Stealth checks without cover or concealment). If she&rsquo;s successful, the opponent&rsquo;s attack hits an inanimate object that the attacker mistook for the ninja, and the ninja may move into an adjacent square and is hidden from the attacker.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Ki Power"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"immediate"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":"1"},"tag":"ninjutsuReplacement","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"attack":{},"identifiedName":"Ki Power: Replacement"},"flags":{"importid":"G9Hx8kX9SdmUZPsm"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"5evnhUu7OoJZuzmZ","name":"Ninja Trick","type":"feat","flags":{"importid":"xoApxDVUeBGRYNJS"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Starting at 2nd level, a ninja gains one ninja trick. She gains one additional ninja trick for every 2 levels attained after 2nd. Unless otherwise noted, a ninja cannot select an individual ninja trick more than once. Talents marked with an asterisk add effects to a ninja&rsquo;s sneak attack. Only one of these talents can be applied to an individual attack, and the decision must be made before the attack roll is made.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A complete list of ninja tricks can be found here:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/ninja-tricks/\">Ninja Tricks</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>At 12th level, and every two levels thereafter, a ninja can select one of the following master tricks in place of a ninja trick.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A complete list of master tricks can be found here:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/ninja-tricks/#master-tricks\">Master Tricks</a></li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","max":0,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"ninjaTrick","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":