{"_id":"9FyofrGagMcdSAtr","name":"Ki Power: Shadow Split","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite(s):&nbsp;Shadow Clone&nbsp;Ki Power</p>\n<p><br />This ninjutsu allows the ninja to create an illusory double of herself that moves away from her, allowing the ninja to create a distraction. When she uses this ability, an illusory double appears and moves away from the ninja, heading in one direction. The double climbs walls, jumps pits, or simply passes through obstacles, moving at twice the ninja&rsquo;s speed in the direction indicated by the ninja when the ability is used. Its course cannot be changed. The double persists for 1 round per level of the ninja. Those who interact with the double receive a Will saving throw to recognize that it is fake. The DC of this save is 10 + half of the ninja&rsquo;s level + her Wisdom modifier. Each use of this ability uses up 1 ki point.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Ki Power "]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":"@classes.ninja.lvl","units":"minute"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"actionType":"save","ability":{"damage":"","damageMult":1,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":"10+floor(@classes.ninja.lvl/2)+@abilities.wis.mod","type":"will","description":"To recognize fake"},"tag":"ninjutsuShadowSplit","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"abilityType":"su","attack":{},"identifiedName":"Ki Power: Shadow Split"},"flags":{"importid":"ahMTTT7AD8Jx6G9G"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"9aopYa9q8vvi7WQW","name":"Ki Power: Shadow Clone","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>The ninja can create 1d4 shadowy duplicates of herself that conceal her true location. This ability functions as&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/m/mirror-image\">Mirror Image</a>, using the ninja&rsquo;s level as her caster level. Using this ability is a standard action that uses up 1 ki point.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Ki Power"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":"@classes.ninja.lvl","units":"minute"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"tag":"ninjutsuShadowClone","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"abilityType":"su","attack":{},"identifiedName":"Ki Power: Shadow Clone"},"flags":{"importid":"6i1RJYzdMShrGxGO"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"name":"Ninja Trick, Master: Bomb Master (Su)","type":"feat","flags":{"importid":"sBjpW15fPRedUsL4"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"9boxogHmTlMWBbZ2","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#ninja-tricks\">Ninja Trick</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Bomb Master (Su)<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span></p>\n<p>Prerequisite(s): Choking Bomb, Poison Bomb, Smoke Bomb ninja tricks</p>\n<p>The ninja has learned enough of the alchemical secrets of bombmaking to gain additional effects when using smoke bombs. The ninja may select any one of the following chemist discoveries (from the chemist class) and apply it to her smoke bombs: delayed bomb, dispelling bomb, plague bomb, stink bomb, tanglefoot bomb. The ninja cannot combine a dispelling bomb, plague bomb, stink bomb, tanglefoot bomb with a choking bomb, but can combine them with a blinding bomb.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","max":0,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"bombMasterSu","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","o