{"_id":"FFUF98BcoiQAVupl","name":"Ki Power: Advanced Healing Technique","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite(s): Healing Technique Ki Power&nbsp;<br /><br />The ninja has learned to focus her ki into a subject&rsquo;s pressure points, allowing for rapid stimulation of a target&rsquo;s own healing abilities. The ninja may make a Heal check to provide first aid, treat a wound, or treat poison as a swift action or move action. A ninja may make a Heal check to treat a disease, tend to a creature wounded by a spike growth or spike stones spell, treat deadly wounds, or provide long-term care as a standard action. A ninja must have at least 1 ki point to use this Ki Power.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Ki Power "]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"tag":"ninjutsuAdvancedHealingTechnique","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"abilityType":"su","attack":{},"identifiedName":"Ki Power: Advanced Healing Technique"},"flags":{"importid":"aNz8dzk35fVpB4XK"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
