{"name":"Ninja Trick, Master: Blinding Bomb (Ex)","type":"feat","flags":{"importid":"yl1b3jDh49LSbdcr"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"IwGFaJvWFw6F1fvB","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#ninja-tricks\">Ninja Trick</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Blinding Bomb (Ex)</p>\n<p>Prerequisite(s): Choking Bomb ninja trick</p>\n<p>Whenever the ninja throws a smoke bomb, all living creatures in the cloud must make a Fortitude save or be blinded by the black smoke for 1d4 rounds. The DC of this saving throw is equal to 10 + half of the ninja&rsquo;s level + her Wisdom modifier. This trick cannot be combined with a choking bomb, but the ninja can combine a blinding bomb with a poison bomb.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","max":0,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"blindingBombEx","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[