{"name":"Ninja Trick: Two with One Blow (Ex)","type":"feat","flags":{"importid":"3vYIOf5KCUn9YtDg"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"K5CRIwchs3RhouRi","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#ninja-tricks\">Ninja Trick</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Two with One Blow (Ex)</p>\n<p>If a ninja with this ninja trick uses a thrown weapon to attack two opponents adjacent to each other at once by taking a -4 penalty on the attack roll. The attack may hit either, both, or neither opponent depending on the roll and the Armor Class of each opponent. Damage for each opponent is resolved separately. If the attack roll results in the threat of a critical hit, roll to confirm each critical hit separately. This trick can be used on any thrown weapon attacks during a full attack action.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","max":0,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"twoWithOneBlowEx","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","