{"_id":"O24j4SB0AjgiJBUW","name":"Ki Power: Faceless Shroud","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>This allows the ninja to disappear for 1 round per ninja level (max of 5). This ability functions as&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/d/disappear\">Disappear</a>. Using this Ki Power uses up 1 ki point.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Ki Power "]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":"min(5,@classes.ninja.lvl)","units":"round"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"tag":"ninjutsuFacelessShroud","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"abilityType":"su","attack":{},"identifiedName":"Ki Power: Faceless Shroud"},"flags":{"importid":"tfmPyerl4MChvQkT"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"O4te8wNUe7Em4jE2","name":"Ki Power: Improved Ki","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>The ninja has improved the ki powers possessed by all ninja.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>As long as she has at least 1 point in her ki pool, she gains a bonus to all Acrobatics skill checks made to jump equal to half her level.</li>\n<li>By spending 2 points from her ki pool, a ninja can make two additional attacks at her highest attack bonus with a -2 penalty to all attacks, but she can do so only when making a full attack.</li>\n<li>In addition, she can spend 2 points to increase her speed by 40 feet for 1 round.</li>\n<li>Finally, a ninja can spend 2 points from her ki pool to give herself a +8 insight bonus on Stealth checks for [[1*@cl]] rounds.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Each of these powers is activated as a swift action.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Ki Power"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"swift"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"tag":"ninjutsuImprovedKi","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"showInQuickbar":true,"abilityType":"su","attack":{},"identifiedName":"Ki Power: Improved Ki"},"flags":{"importid":"D6oY3NeTIQchezkm"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"O7xqrj03XrNnH0gc","name":"Ki Power: Concealment","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A ninja can harness his ki to cause an attack against him to miss when it might otherwise hit. When a ninja can spend 1 ki point to activate this ability, his outline shifts and wavers, granting him concealment (20% miss chance), against all attacks for 1 round per ninja level.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Ki Power "]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":"@classes.ninja.lvl","units":"round"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"tag":"ninjutsuConcealment","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"abilityType":"su","attack":{},"identifiedName":"Ki Power: Concealment"},"flags":{"importid":"RoUOyhbZuyXCVh5E"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"OTcoKiwJPpxB5gug","name":"Talent Trees: DWS Unending Flurry","type":"feat","flags":{"importid":"xoApxDVUeBGRYNJS"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Unending Flurry:&nbsp;At a cost of 20 stamina points, as a swift action, the nightblade doubles his amount of attacks in the round against one target. If the target is affected by immobilize from Low Blow, all attacks gain a bonus equal to the nightblade&rsquo;s Wisdom modifier. Cannot be used in conjunction with Dual Striking.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Prerequisites:&nbsp;Twin Strikes, Low Blow, Find Vitals</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","max":0,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"ninjaTrick","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRang