{"name":"Ninjutsu","type":"feat","flags":{"importid":"PY9Y9Es3B82tuZfl"},"img":"systems/ffd20/icons/FFxiv-icons/FFXIVIcons-Battle(PvE)/09_NIN/ninjutsu.png","_id":"ZfVtCJpyncJcRhr9","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>As a ninja continues her training, she learns ninjutsu that allow her to confuse her foes and grant her supernatural abilities. Starting at 3rd level and every two ninja levels thereafter, a ninja learns a new ninjutsu from the list below. Some ninjutsu have prerequisites. Unless otherwise noted, a ninja cannot select an individual ninjutsu more than once.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A complete list of ninjutsu can be found here:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/ninjutsu/\">Ninjutsu</a></li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","max":0,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"ninjutsuAccelerationOfForm","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"