{"name":"Talent Trees","type":"feat","flags":{"importid":"xoApxDVUeBGRYNJS"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"cqapi7Y4jqdsGYja","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>The nightblade gets access to the dual weapon and double blades talent trees from below. At 2nd level and every two levels thereafter, the nightblade may choose to learn one talent or a ninja trick taken from the ninja&rsquo;s @Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-ninja.5evnhUu7OoJZuzmZ]{Ninja Trick}. The <span lang=\"en-US\">nightblade</span>&nbsp;may pick up Extra&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">Ninja Trick</span>&nbsp;feats to select these talents.&nbsp;Weapon Requirement:&nbsp;Any two&nbsp;light melee weapons (not unarmed strikes).</p>\n<p><strong>Dual Weapon Specialization Talent Tree</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-ninja.xaGlVEGmJM0ukvXh]{Talent Trees: DWS Dual-Weapon Finesse}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-ninja.BmxRaNhMZ9ynRaXd]{Talent Trees: DWS Dual-Weapon Expert}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-ninja.rgnDIgqDxybjKR9M]{Talent Trees: DWS Dual Striking}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-ninja.w12JOrrdb6hwwBjT]{Talent Trees: DWS Flurry}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-ninja.z07PB6jj6hsIRGKk]{Talent Trees: DWS Dual-Weapon Sweep}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-ninja.vE2SIB0mKwkxHQzE]{Talent Trees: DWS Whirlwind}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-ninja.F0EEFGggYnRJ1TOr]{Talent Trees: DWS Twin Strikes}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-ninja.T5Lrl1zB0KebVb1P]{Talent Trees: DWS Low Blow}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-ninja.87Tcnhdp85CNmG1z]{Talent Trees: DWS Find Vitals}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-ninja.OTcoKiwJPpxB5gug]{Talent Trees: DWS Unending Flurry}</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Double Blades Specialization Talent Tree</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[ffd