{"_id":"gLeXb0HILZGgCk2z","name":"Ki Power: Greater Ki Blade","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite(s): Ki Blade Ki Power<br /><br />When a ninja spends a ki point to grant an enhancement bonus to a weapon she is holding using the ki blade ninjutsu, these bonuses can be used to add any of the following weapon properties: dancing, flaming, flaming burst, frost, icy burst, keen, shock, shocking burst, speed, or vorpal. Adding these properties consumes an amount of bonus equal to the property&rsquo;s base price modifier. These properties are added to any the weapon already has, but duplicates do not stack. If the weapon is not magical, at least a +1 enhancement bonus must be added before any other properties can be added. These bonuses and properties are decided when the ki point is spent and cannot be changed until the next time the ninja uses this ability.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Ki Power "]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"special"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"tag":"ninjutsuGreaterKiBlade","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"attack":{},"identifiedName":"Ki Power: Greater Ki Blade"},"flags":{"importid":"I2CerMcB4fn7naOz"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"glHNb8yHpZZwTiqf","name":"No Trace","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, a ninja learns to cover her tracks, remain hidden, and conceal her presence. The DC to track a ninja using the Survival skill increases by +[[floor((@classes.ninja.lvl+2)/3)]]. In addition, her training gives her a +[[floor((@classes.ninja.lvl+2)/3)]]&nbsp;insight bonus on Disguise skill checks and on opposed Stealth checks whenever she is stationary and does not take any action for at least 1 round.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Every three levels thereafter, the increase to Survival DCs and the bonuses on Disguise and opposed Stealth checks increase by 1. These have been adjusted above</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","max":0,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[{"text":"The DC to track a ninja using the Survival skill increases by +[[floor((@classes.ninja.lvl+2)/3)]]","target":"skill","subTarget":"skill.ste"},{"text":"+[[floor((@classes.ninja.lvl+2)/3)]] insight bonus on Disguise skill checks and on opposed Stealth checks whenever she is stationary and does not take any action for at least 1 round.","target":"skill","subTarget":"skill.dis"},{"text":"+[[floor((@classes.ninja.lvl+2)/3)]] insight bonus on Disguise skill checks and on opposed Stealth checks whenever she is stationary and does not take any action for at least 1 round.","target":"skill","subTarget":"skill.ste"}],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"showI