{"_id":"oCOcvMuznfKlfL7u","name":"Ninja Trick, Master: Accomplished Sneak Attacker","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#ninja-tricks\">Ninja Trick</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>A ninja with this trick increases the amount of sneak attack damage dealt by 1d6. This cannot increase the amount of sneak attack damage dice beyond half of her ninja level (maximum 10d6). This ninja trick can be selected up to three times.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Ninja Trick, Master"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"tag":"ninjaTrickMasterImprovedEvasionEx","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"attack":{},"identifiedName":"Ninja Trick, Master: Accomplished Sneak Attacker"},"flags":{"importid":"PeQraOvaUhrJzZQ2"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"name":"Ninjutsu: Master Disguise","type":"feat","flags":{"importid":"pVERCMgdexQEXFMJ"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"pGNSmpIDARcwTf6p","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite(s):&nbsp;Sudden Disguise ninjutsu<br /><br />A ninja with this ninjutsu can take on the appearance of other creatures and individuals. Whenever the ninja uses the sudden disguise ninjutsu, the duration increases to 10 minutes per level. Alternatively, the ninja can use the sudden disguise ninjutsu to take on the appearance of a specific individual that the ninja has seen before for 1 minute per level. Creatures that are familiar with the individual receive a Will saving throw to see through the illusion. The DC of this saving throw is 10 + half of the ninja&rsquo;s level + her Wisdom modifier. This illusion also changes the ninja&rsquo;s speech, if she has heard the individual talk and can speak his language.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","max":0,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"ninjutsuMasterDisguise","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":fals