{"_id":"sMurhK4aWFYvebsl","name":"Ki Power: Invisible Blade","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite(s): Ninja 11th level, Faceless Shroud Ki Power<br /><br />Whenever a ninja uses the faceless shroud Ki Power, she is treated as if she were under the effects of greater vanish.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Ki Power"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"special"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"tag":"ninjutsuInvisibleBlade","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"abilityType":"su","attack":{},"identifiedName":"Ki Power: Invisible Blade"},"flags":{"importid":"hcKHbONZsqmxC3YE"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"name":"Ninja Trick, Master: All the Stars in the Sky (Ex)","type":"feat","flags":{"importid":"1smNEEjN1wb62925"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"sWzzE6unVLnTAmET","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/hybrid-classes/ninja/#ninja-tricks\">Ninja Trick</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>All the Stars in the Sky (Ex)</p>\n<p><span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>Certain master ninjas possess a seemingly limitless supply of their trusted weapons. Whenever a ninja with this trick buys a set of 50 identical magic shuriken, she thereafter replenishes them at no cost and never runs out. This stock of magical shuriken can be upgraded as though it were a normal magic weapon, and shuriken upgraded this way likewise never run out.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","max":0,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"allTheStarsInTheSkyEx","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critP