{"_id":"tNBH52luoQbTxvkn","name":"Ki Power: Feign Death","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite(s):&nbsp;Slow Metabolism ninja trick<br /><br />The ninja can slow her metabolic rate by such a vast degree she enters a deathlike state. The ninja is treated as being asleep while in this trance, though she may decide to automatically awaken after a set period of time. If the ninja is examined while in this trace, the examiner must make a Heal check (DC 15 + ninja&rsquo;s level) to realize the ninja is not dead. While in this trance, the ninja can hold her breath for twenty times as long as normal before needing to make Constitution checks. A ninja must have at least 1 ki point to use this Ki Power.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Ki Power "]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"tag":"ninjutsuFeignDeath","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"abilityType":"ex","attack":{},"identifiedName":"Ki Power: Feign Death"},"flags":{"importid":"XXPXoG72ZMR2YO0I"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
