{"_id":"x5hTfF1JqEeb7S1M","name":"Ki Power: Feather Fall","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>As an immediate action, the ninja can slow her descent as if using&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/c/choco-feather\">Choco Feather</a>. This ability uses her ninja level as the caster level. Each use of this ability uses up 1 ki point.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"immediate"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"tag":"ninjutsuFeatherFall","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"abilityType":"su","attack":{},"identifiedName":"Ki Power: Feather Fall"},"flags":{"importid":"uoJFB6FUcXp6tyUX"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"x7PRXECg9td8gc8x","name":"Death Mark","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 5th level, as a swift action once per day, a ninja can mark an opponent damaged by her sneak attack for death. A ninja gains a +[[Floor(@classes.ninja.lvl/5)]] competence bonus on attack and damage rolls against an opponent affected by death mark as well as on Survival checks to track the marked creature. The effects of death mark last for 24 hours, until the marked creature is slain, or until the ninja chooses to mark another creature, whichever comes first.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Sneak Attack"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"swift"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":"1","units":"day"},"target":{"value":"an opponent damaged by her sneak attack"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":"Floor(@classes.ninja.lvl/5)"},"tag":"lightSteps","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ninja"]]},"attack":{},"identifiedName":"Death Mark"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"xXB7OcQkAOgTEvWK","name":"Slicing Wind","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 20th level, the ninja is a creature of wind and blades.</p>\n<p>As a full-round action like normal Light Steps, she can move up to four times her speed, ignoring difficult terrain. While moving in this way, any surface will support her, no matter how much she weighs. This allows her to move across water, lava, or even the thinnest tree branches. She must end her move on a surface that can support her normally. She cannot move across air in this way, nor can she walk up walls or other vertical surfaces. When moving in this way, she does not take damage from surfaces or hazards that react to being touched, such as lava or caltrops, nor does she need to make Acrobatics checks to avoid falling on slippery or rough surfaces. Finally, when using light steps, the ninja ignores any mechanical traps that use a location-based trigger. And she may make a single attack at her highest base attack bonus at any point during the movement.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[{"_id":"WEbj3iRXZv9zhRsW","name":"Use","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","description":"","tag":"","activation":{"cost":1,"type":"full"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","self":{"value":0,"maxFormula":"","per":null},"per":"","value":0,"maxFormula":"","max":0},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack